# App Flow Document: Sparq

## Introduction

This document provides a clear and straightforward overview of the Sparq app, a mobile-first platform designed to help couples and individuals improve their emotional, sexual, and communicative connections. The app guides users through AI-driven relationship coaching, dynamic meditation sessions, focus-enhancing interactions, and customizable activities tailored to diverse relationship types. The journey begins with a warm welcome and detailed onboarding, and it progresses through core features, profile customization, interactive activities, premium upgrades, and settings management. Every step is designed with cultural inclusivity, data privacy, and ease of use in mind.

## Onboarding and Sign-In/Sign-Up

New users are welcomed by an inviting onboarding screen featuring a warm, gradient background that sets an emotional and trustworthy tone. The initial page prompts them to select their relationship type, whether monogamous, polyamorous, LGBTQ+ or other variants, and includes a straightforward age verification process required for accessing explicit content. Users are guided through creating an account using either email and password or social logins through providers like Google, Facebook, and Apple ID. Detailed forms explain privacy and data use, and clear instructions are provided if the user needs to recover a lost password or sign out from the app. This stage ensures that users feel confident and informed right from their first interaction with Sparq.

## Main Dashboard or Home Page

After successful onboarding and authentication, users are taken to the home dashboard which serves as the central hub of the app. The dashboard displays a daily question carousel with AI-generated summaries designed to inspire meaningful conversations. Users see information on shared progress, such as daily streaks and earned Spark Points, presented with dynamic animations and engaging visual cues. The layout is split to reflect shared experiences between partners where relevant, and navigation menus offer quick access to all core modules including profile setup, activity pages, AI coaching, the focus timer, premium content, and in-app purchases. The dashboard is intentionally designed to be both aesthetically pleasing and functionally clear, enabling users to explore every part of the app with ease.

## Detailed Feature Flows and Page Transitions

Once on the dashboard, users can explore a range of interactive features organized into distinct modules. The profile setup flow allows users to customize their relationship profiles by choosing avatars that represent inclusive body types and by adding personalized details about their relationship preferences. A step-by-step wizard guides them through privacy settings and customizable options to tailor the experience to their cultural and personal needs. Navigation flows seamlessly between the profile setup and the activity pages, which include a Question Hub filled with daily challenges, a Conflict Resolution module offering guided exercises to overcome disagreements, and a Meditation Library where AI-generated audio sessions are presented in themed categories for stress relief and connection building. Additionally, the AI Coaching interface presents a chat-style environment where real-time tone analysis and proactive suggestions are delivered, ensuring that users receive immediate feedback in a friendly format. A dedicated Focus Timer page enforces a distraction-free environment by syncing native Do Not Disturb settings, displaying a full-screen countdown timer and summarizing key session themes at the end. For users seeking an enhanced experience, separate premium and referral pages present subscription options, explicit content modules, and detailed benefits in a visually distinct manner. The in-app store integrates purchase flows that allow users to buy custom meditations and specific AI coaching sessions, anchored to native mobile purchase systems as well as web-based options through Stripe. Transitions between pages are smooth and intuitive, ensuring that users can easily return to the main dashboard or navigate to any section without confusion.

## Settings and Account Management

The Settings section of Sparq is designed to give users full control over their personal information and application preferences. Here, users can update their profile details, manage privacy settings, and adjust notifications and accessibility options such as dark mode and font sizes. Advanced options include secure data deletion processes with clear messages informing users if shared partner data is affected. Users can also access billing information and subscription management details on this page, ensuring transparency and ease of use. The design of the settings area is minimalistic yet comprehensive, allowing users to quickly update or revise their information and then return effortlessly to the main app flow.

## Error States and Alternate Paths

The application includes robust error handling to cover scenarios such as invalid data entry, network connectivity issues, or restricted actions. If a user enters incorrect login details or submits incomplete registration forms, clear error messages appear explaining what needs to be corrected without interrupting the overall flow. In cases of network or server errors, fallback pages are provided that gently inform users of temporary issues and offer retry options. Additionally, if a user attempts to access restricted content without meeting age verification requirements, helpful prompts guide them toward resolving the issue. These alternate paths and error states are designed in everyday language to minimize frustration and keep the user on track towards a successful interaction with the app.

## Conclusion and Overall App Journey

From the moment a new user encounters the warm, inviting onboarding screen to the daily interactions on the main dashboard, Sparq is designed to support and enhance relationship growth through AI-powered insights and engaging activities. Every page, from profile setup to advanced modules like AI coaching, includes clear guidance and fluid transitions, ensuring a seamless experience that resonates with users on both emotional and practical levels. The process culminates in meaningful interactions supported by secure settings and proactive error management, creating an overall app journey that is both intuitive and deeply impactful. Sparq empowers users to deepen their connections, continuously grow through personalized feedback, and easily navigate a comprehensive suite of features designed to enrich their relationships.
